Xmas but make it #cyberpunk 🤖 ➡️ I asked @catalystlatex if they had anything that would fit a Christmas cyberpunk theme 🥺 their designers and team understood the assignment and came up with this incredible outfit. I really can't recommend them enough, from amazing fit, to great quality latex, responsiveness - I only really work with brands I really admire and I am so pleased to say Catalyst really are outstanding in what they do ❤️ if you want something really special, good quality and amazing customer service I really can't recommend them enough! 😻❤️

The collection is coming together nicely. I started documenting the constant changes of the graffiti art at the Banksy Tunnel, Leake Street. Always from the same spot and same puddle. The first was shot on my old Nikon in 2018, then the rest was taken on my @sonyalpha in 2019, 2021 and 2023. Merch of this collection will be available soon 🔜

Since then, I take the same image from the same puddle every now and then to showcase the different art, colors and styles. Walking around the tunnel feels like you are inside of a living art piece. An experience no other location can replicate. Which one is your favourite photo of the series?
